ggplot(data = 
    mf_df_scan4
    .with_columns(
        pl.col('Loan Acquisition UPB').str.replace_all(r"$|,","").alias('Loan Acquisition UPB')
        )
    .with_columns(pl.col('Loan Acquisition UPB').str.lstrip("$").alias('Loan Acquisition UPB')
                  .cast(pl.Float64)
                  )
    .select('Loan Number','Loan Acquisition UPB','Property City','Property State')
    .unique()
    
    .with_columns(state_count = pl.count().over('Property State'))
    .with_columns((pl.col('Property State') + "(" + pl.col('state_count').cast(pl.Utf8) + ")").alias('Property State'))
    
    .rename({"Loan Acquisition UPB":"Loan_Acquisition_UPB",
             "Property State":"Property_State"})
    .collect()

                  y = "Loan_Acquisition_UPB",
                  color = "Property_State"))
    + geom_boxplot()
    + coord_flip()
    # + geom_jitter()
    + theme_538()
    + theme(legend_position="none",
            figure_size=(8, 15))
    + labs(title = "Loan Origination Value by States")
)
